do CinematicManager.play_cinematic(PlayerManager.player, "_CinematicIdle/CinematicIdle_Down")
do wait(1.0)
do CinematicManager.play_cinematic(PlayerManager.player, "_CinematicIdle/CinematicIdle_Right")
do wait(1.0)
do CinematicManager.play_cinematic(PlayerManager.player, "_CinematicIdle/CinematicIdle_Up")
do wait(1.0)
Mi cabeza está mejor, pero esas voces, esas sombras...
do wait(1.0)
